        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "晴，你的义肢——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是我最关心的事情，在我的印象中，我离开时晴的右手应该还是正常的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "晴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊，这没什么……在此之前，分析员，由于我今天给安全部新兵训练，到这里时迟到了两分三十三秒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "晴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以我可以满足你一个要求……嗯，当然，得是合理的要求。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "晴说完，很认真地盯着我，等待我提出要求。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "果然性格也还是老样子。",
        "disable": 0
